  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p>1. Provides secretarial services to Director of Sales and Marketing.</p>\n<p>2. Provides administrative and clerical support to the sales team.</p>\n<p>3. Files report, forward phone calls, reply emails, handle customer inquiries.</p>\n<p>4. Conducts site inspection in the absence of Sales Manager.</p>\n<p>5. Schedules and coordinates management meetings and appointments with the various departments.</p>\n<p>6. Coordinates transfer arrangements for corporate groups and prepares welcome letters for long-stay guests and ad hoc groups.</p>\n<p>7. Prepares confirmation letters for group bookings.</p>\n<p>8. Generates and maintains clients’ database.</p>\n<p>9. Responsible for the flow of information and correspondence related to the Sales and Marketing Department internally and externally.</p>\n<p>10. Performs any other duties and responsibilities as and when assigned by the Management.</p>",
